gs so as not to gain negative points. once the last card in one of the decks is played the game is over and the player with the most points wins!</p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='text-muted'>This page does not exist. You can edit this page to create it.</span>","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"7984439","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__small/img/K5wri4Ssp_lh9euF2iiEjDVidQg=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__micro/img/1k3YeUWIHh1eG-4DHrPY2m4dZMc=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__square/img/JcNp3TOx0LpEPmh1QHb5jBhvMlw=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__tallthumb/img/vCdICdpeLWU6H83Jta7Otmi3p90=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__previewthumb/img/pzPOuv1uoIxlZXcZ4MQxlIwmRY8=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__square200/img/Ss_D_AVBE_9tZXiYIurukWue9dY=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__original/img/LsQIlWnTpxlAFcZv6np69p-h-6M=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic7984439.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/7984439/sosig","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__itemrep/img/UPdiU4r53uYLuw099aXP5hC3-P8=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","imageurl@2x":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__itemrep@2x/img/zStvKoGFFTiZm3evdXTbm639ZVU=/fit-in/492x600/filters:strip_icc()/pic7984439.jpg","topimageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/gsC5CNj1Wnmwdsrad9q72A__itemheader/img/hwoda-2hnofoIzm_iHfhelRLlMM=/800x450/filters:quality(30):strip_icc()/pic8256006.jpg","imageSets":{"square100":{"src":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/nUqbZVErXXHzqCTMWsMonA__